    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Hoptale》中文是《跳跃传说》，是一款核心为『跳房子 × 老虎机』的 Roguelite。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以跳房子进行探索、采集、钓鱼、解谜；<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/a9ae2def2730f754ea884f4197a3ee82.poster.avif?t=1765949448\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/a9ae2def2730f754ea884f4197a3ee82.webm?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/a9ae2def2730f754ea884f4197a3ee82.mp4?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗时，格子化为老虎机，必须锁定安全的道路才能击败怪物；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/eaab4ba23a961b34309e630d560c0687.poster.avif?t=1765949448\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/eaab4ba23a961b34309e630d560c0687.webm?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/eaab4ba23a961b34309e630d560c0687.mp4?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >连战利品与收获，也由老虎机决定，命运尽在你的反应力！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/13ee8febdaf9c9b03fc85afb9d934d00.poster.avif?t=1765949448\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/13ee8febdaf9c9b03fc85afb9d934d00.webm?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/13ee8febdaf9c9b03fc85afb9d934d00.mp4?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事背景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事将从主角的村庄开始，拯救被邪神教徒抓捕、失踪的村民和妹妹，一路上邂逅各个角色！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/9817a32db60db0682f2c518b7cffdaf3.poster.avif?t=1765949448\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/9817a32db60db0682f2c518b7cffdaf3.webm?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/9817a32db60db0682f2c518b7cffdaf3.mp4?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这片已经被邪神侵蚀的大地上，与各个强大BOSS们对战！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/b4ffd55ca1adb0ca26fcd4a4cbb131ab.poster.avif?t=1765949448\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/b4ffd55ca1adb0ca26fcd4a4cbb131ab.webm?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/b4ffd55ca1adb0ca26fcd4a4cbb131ab.mp4?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/816fdaca491b64800247cd3dd74d3e40.poster.avif?t=1765949448\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/816fdaca491b64800247cd3dd74d3e40.webm?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/816fdaca491b64800247cd3dd74d3e40.mp4?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩大基地、新增可选角色，体验各种不同的格子效果，组合出千奇百怪的流派！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/a0e662abd4a8ee5ff3537ae43b2fb179.poster.avif?t=1765949448\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/a0e662abd4a8ee5ff3537ae43b2fb179.webm?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/a0e662abd4a8ee5ff3537ae43b2fb179.mp4?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >冒险途中的事件</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/d0e6c7f9fea2d87e780afb4187e1be1d.poster.avif?t=1765949448\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/d0e6c7f9fea2d87e780afb4187e1be1d.webm?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/d0e6c7f9fea2d87e780afb4187e1be1d.mp4?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险的旅途中也可能遭遇到BOSS的追杀，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但但但先别慌！说...说不定逃着逃着就捡到神装宝物了(？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗、商店、采集、甚至是强化，全都用老虎机结果来决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/c8a47f81858f201f62a02d306f1e28e1.poster.avif?t=1765949448\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/c8a47f81858f201f62a02d306f1e28e1.webm?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/c8a47f81858f201f62a02d306f1e28e1.mp4?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要你的反应够快，就能化不可能为可能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/abaf0dc217bc0e13a4643fcc1063cb10.poster.avif?t=1765949448\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074730/extras/abaf0dc217bc0e13a4643fcc1063cb10.webm?t=1765949448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >总之，先加个愿望清单吧！(拜托)</h2>",
